# Sprint 3.1 – Phase 3: Authentication Business Logic Implementation Plan

This implementation plan details the redesign and implementation of the **Authentication Business Logic** layer. The core service `backend/app/services/auth_service.py` will be rebuilt as a clean, stateless orchestration service completely decoupled from FastAPI dependencies and SQLAlchemy model leakage.

